  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink275-kilavi">varaiyātu vantoḻukum talaimakaṉ iṭaiyiṭṭu varutalāl etirppāṭu peṟāta tōḻi etirppaṭṭ avaṉ koṭumai kūṟi neruṅkic colliyatu.
          </p>
        <p xml:lang="en"> What the confidante, who had not [yet] obtained a meeting [with the hero], said, having encountered and approached [him], speaking of his cruelty, because the hero—who kept coming without marrying—came intermittently.           
          
        </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink275">
<l>kuraṅkiṉ ṟalaivaṉ kurumayirk kaṭuvaṉ</l>
<l>cūralañ ciṟukōl koṇṭu viyalaṟai</l>
<l>māri mokkuḷ puṭaikku nāṭa</l>
<l>yāṉiṉ ṉayantaṉa meṉiṉumem</l>
<l>māynalam vāṭumō varuḷuti yeṉiṉē</l>
</lg>
<lg xml:lang="en">
  <l>O man from the land </l>
  <l rend="space">where a monkey with brilliant fur,</l>
  <l>leader of the monkeys,</l>
  <l>taking a stick, pierces the rainwater bubbles</l>
  <l>on a wide rock—</l>
  <l rend="space">we have longed for you. Even so, if you were to grace us,</l>
  <l>would our choice beauty fade?</l>

  
</lg>
</div>
</body>
